This is an APP that enables direct communication with ChatGPT from your device. The communication generated by the APP does not pass through any intermediate servers before reaching ChatGPT. However, please note that your email address will be shared with ChatGPT along with your requests for usage monitoring. For more information about the data privacy practices of ChatGPT, please refer to their privacy policy available at the following link: ChatGPT Privacy Policy.

I hereby state, to the best of my knowledge and belief, that I have not programmed this app to collect any personally identifiable information. All data, including app preferences (such as theme settings) and alarms, created by you (the user) is stored locally on your device only. If you wish to remove this data, you can simply clear the app's data or uninstall it.

To provide the functionality of saving and loading images and files, the app requires access to your device's storage. This access is necessary solely for the purpose of managing these specific app-related files.

It's important to note that the APP contacts ChatGPT via an API over HTTPS, ensuring that the communication is encrypted for enhanced security and privacy.

Please review and familiarize yourself with this privacy policy. If you have any concerns or questions regarding the privacy of your data, please feel free to contact us.

The App require the following permissions:
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE" />
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE" />
    
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />
     to Access ChatGPT directly 
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE" />
      To check network connectivty and informs you when there is an issue with internet connectivity 
      
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE" />
      To save images and files generated by the app on local storage    
        
